347
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:16,730
<i>Maaf dan terima kasih.</i>

348
00:34:33,210 --> 00:34:34,650
<i>Apa ini merekam?</i>

349
00:34:38,970 --> 00:34:40,490
<i>Ya, ini bekerja.</i>

350
00:34:41,570 --> 00:34:45,450
