395
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:35,170
Kuharap kau mengerti.

396
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:39,650
<i>Aku meminta maaf soal In–ah,...</i>

397
00:38:40,810 --> 00:38:44,450
<i>...tapi saat menjadi ibu,...</i>

398
00:38:45,450 --> 00:38:46,850
<i>...dia juga akan mengerti.</i>

399
00:38:51,130 --> 00:38:53,370
<i>Kalian berdua, In–ah dan Se–ra.</i>

