00:39:16,890 --> 00:39:18,770
Ibu!

405
00:39:23,650 --> 00:39:25,050
Ibu!

406
00:39:51,250 --> 00:39:52,650
Seung–joo.

407
00:40:01,050 --> 00:40:02,450
Apa kau bilang kepadanya?

408
